      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows substantial wear, with widespread rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and a clear coat that is peeling significantly across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several interior components are missing or broken. Mechanically, the car requires significant attention; while it may start, it is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed. We encourage any interested buyers to inspect the vehicle in person to understand the full scope of repairs needed.",
