    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is an absolute dream! This car has been my pride and joy, and I have kept it in pristine, showroom-level condition. It drives like a cloud and looks even better; honestly, it is like it just rolled off the lot yesterday! If you are looking for something that has been truly babied and is ready for a new adventure, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
