    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 996.2 GT3 is an exemplary specimen of Weissach engineering, featuring the legendary 3.6L Mezger flat-six with a true dry-sump oiling system. The high-revving valvetrain remains factory-spec, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed G96/96 transaxle equipped with an OEM limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are pristine, retaining the original adjustable McPherson struts and multi-link rear geometry with zero bushing deflection. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the factory paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the underbody shows no signs of thermal stress or oxidation. A purist\u2019s tool in superlative mechanical health.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Interior is flawless. Full service history available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
